Class BasicNumericDataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.tm.stindex.spatial.sfc.data.BasicNumericDataset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexConstraints, Persistable, MultiDimensionalNumericData

    public class BasicNumericDataset
extends java.lang.Object
implements MultiDimensionalNumericData
    The Basic Index Result class creates an object associated with a generic query. This class can be used when the dimensions and/or axis are generic.
